is
being
prosecuted
by
Mr.
Athelney
Jones,
of
Scotland
Yard,
with
all
his
well
known
energy
and
sagacity.
Further
arrests
may
be
expected
at
any
moment."
"That
is
satisfactory
so
far
as
it
goes,"
thought
I.
"Friend
Sholto
is
safe,
at
any
rate.
